<Container className="container">
  <Slider className="employees" {...settings}>
    {alliances.map((alliance) => {
      return (
        <React.Fragment>
          <Col style={{ display: "flex", flexDirection: "row" }} s>
            <Team key={alliance.id} alliance={alliance} />
          </Col>
        </React.Fragment>
      );
    })}
  </Slider>
</Container>;
